Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:10.65,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:47.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:52.82,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta mustered up everything he had \Nand used it on this blow to Vetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:00:58.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:03.85,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But the battle wasn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:08.05,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you all down with me... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:11.21,main,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow this whole temple to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:13.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:16.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Right, consider it brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:23.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dumbasses. You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.39,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:28.56,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Accepting all the feelings of \NAsta and the other members,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:31.32,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami dealt a fatal blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:35.69,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how strong your magic is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:41.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked Dimension Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:50.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Consider that my thanks for \Nlooking after my squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:53.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Mister Despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:57.26,flashbackitalics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there and watch for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.64,flashbackitalics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be my main dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:04.78,flashbackitalics,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,After I season you with despair, \Nas you watch all of your friends die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:08.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I dealt with you in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:10.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully, you can pass on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:21.03,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I didn't despair at all, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:31.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being led far away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:40.20,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we shatter the road \Nbetween light and darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo Guess who's back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody get down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess who's back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.02,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey step up step up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.65,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,480)}End of the Battle,\NEnd of Despair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:03.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling down because of a twist of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:07.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The harmony we had is in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Still left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:12.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of you is stuck in my head
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't shake it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:19.55,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting just isn't enough anymore, Yai yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.38,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Guess Who is back!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:23.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As I hold on to my wish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:25.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Guess Who is back!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:28.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The roulette points to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Guess Who is back!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:34.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the light shine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.14,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Guess Who is back!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:39.24,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark maze
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:41.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Guess Who is back!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Guess Who is back!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.52,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we seize the hope in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.70,main,Phati,0000,0000,0000,,Heave ho... Heave ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.80,main,Aphro,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! We're going to \Ntake you right to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:09.27,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.56,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha... Bah-ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:18.20,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,That monster's presence... vah-hanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:41.04,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:44.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess you saved us.\NYou should've shown up sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.68,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain! I've fallen \Nfor you all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.35,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're invincible! Absolutely amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.61,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:59.86,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going to die... \NI saw my life flash before my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You were surprisingly useful for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, surprisingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:08.17,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You were amazing, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:11.29,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:11.29,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who were you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.37,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La! You were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you guys fluffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:16.87,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.85,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here, so can I go see Marie now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:24.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Take the hint. You're supposed\Nto praise me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're so awesome, Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It only took one hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:29.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're just so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:46.70,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Yami Sukehiro... \NAnd members of the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.62,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on defeating the \NEye of the Midnight Sun team
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.66,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,and beating the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.83,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:58.32,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you from the bottom of my heart \Nfor saving our Underwater Temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.63,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:07.13,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow me, as the high priest,\Nto grant your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:10.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. So just as we promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:13.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be taking the magic stone that \Nyou have here at the Underwater Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.27,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.14,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,What's the magic stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.73,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:24.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gramps, I thought you\N knew about the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:27.65,flashback,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are after the \Nmagic stone, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:31.59,flashback,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, why don't \Nwe play a little game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.03,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you said, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:36.59,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I just heard you guys talking \Nabout how you were looking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:39.35,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,for something called a "magic stone."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.32,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,It's a "magic stone," so I assume it's a stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.81,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of stone is it? What does it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You old bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.55,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, calm down! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:51.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:55.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt this pain \Nsince Saussy Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nero. I wondered \Nwhere you'd gone off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you were looking \Nfor the magic stone for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:00.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.25,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's the magic stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.24,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all you want, \Nsure, go ahead and take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.51,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,No need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why would we hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll be taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.00,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.54,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:37.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I relaxed, all my strength just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:40.34,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all out of magic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.42,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.87,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:42.87,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.33,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.93,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:50.74,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tend to your wounds and help\Nyou recover your magic and stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.96,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,To think that Vetto was actually defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:10.17,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive them. I will never \Nforgive those who make Licht sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.72,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,We must take back the magic stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:18.91,italics,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,so that we can fulfill our dream as\Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:40.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. I can't believe we have to \Nwait for Finral's magic to recover
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.74,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,before we can go back to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.55,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're so friggin' useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:46.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I have seniority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:51.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So, Grey... It turns out \Nyou're a super cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:55.72,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so embarrassed! \NPlease don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:09:00.38,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If your eyes get any pervier, \NI'm going to sew them shut, Pervy Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:01.23,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:06.04,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And Grey, if you're that embarrassed,\Nyou're never going to make it in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:10.31,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,And you should be a little \Nmore humble, you witch floozy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:14.29,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you embarrassed, virgin delinquent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:15.99,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who you callin' a delinquent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:18.57,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:21.41,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hungry, I can't even move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:23.91,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell is it that you're just hungry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:29.33,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's yummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What really matters here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.71,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,is that we got our asses kicked, so I didn't \Nget to look cool at all, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:39.34,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing we can do about that. \NThis was the full extent of our abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:44.49,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La? Is there a banquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.18,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.81,main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:01.33,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,You're the saviors of the Underwater Temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.24,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.36,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We, the absolute worst \NMagic Knights squad in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:13.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,are being thanked by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:17.95,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, isn't it great?\NI wanna get even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:21.85,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll get even stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.51,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Marie more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.80,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I wasn't so easily embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:29.25,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's hot! That one's great, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.23,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:36.94,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Being thanked by others is pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Kahono.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:46.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend, but I \Ncouldn't protect your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.60,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Noelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:11:02.30,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for protecting my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.83,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:09.64,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you helped \Nme with my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:12.95,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know. You'd better be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:16.94,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Also!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.70,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't given up on my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.61,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can go sing up on the surface again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.62,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure this heals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:32.79,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,So when I'm an idol someday,\Nyou'd better come and hear me sing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:34.07,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Kahono...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:44.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll definitely go, so you'd better \Nsave me the best seat in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.88,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:07.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you should probably get \Nsome rest. I'll come by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:10.03,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Thanks for coming to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:12.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:21.34,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You were awake, Kiato? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:24.06,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,You look goofier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:28.71,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Such beautiful tears... \NAnd such a beautiful smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:33.14,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the sea goddess \Neveryone was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.70,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:38.45,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I'm going to get my leg healed up fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.94,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I have to dance the courtship dance for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.76,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,You have to introduce me to her later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.11,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Help me win her over, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:49.34,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm starting to feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.76,italics,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure Noelle's unavailable, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:06.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We ended up getting the magic stone, \Nbut so much happened that we didn't expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:14.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up! Stop wandering off like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:18.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Don't blame me if you get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're amazing, Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You must've sensed my ki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you what's up, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question or I'll send you flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:56.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... Since we're leaving this place \Ntomorrow, I wanted go exploring a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So I was wandering here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:01.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Just full of energy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:09.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! I found fossilized seashells, almost got\Nswallowed by a giant sea anemone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and got attacked by this insane \Nswarm of wharf roaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to find these pretty flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:42.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:47.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but these guys must've had something \Nthey can't forgive, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:52.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Something that makes them \Nhate humans so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.62,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams? Bonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:15:00.49,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,People like you have no right \Nto talk about such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.96,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:08.17,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you have hope just \Nbecause you've banded together, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:13.21,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that I would \Nlose... against you humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:18.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that maybe he was feeling \Nmore despair than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:35.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I asked if you were an idiot.\NAnswer the question or I'll send you flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Yes! I'm an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:42.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots don't need to think so hard \Nabout stuff like that, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:48.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to keep chasing your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,At least for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:57.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see! And I can't push it back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami! Both of my arms are broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Captain Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:06.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:16.91,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I just need to \Nkeep chasing my dream, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:22.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My dream, no, our dream is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.44,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.95,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I got my own grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:33.13,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's insanely shabby, but I'm gonna take \Ngood care of it for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:37.43,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there, there, there. \NThere, there, there, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:45.06,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repay you for this someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.36,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:51.48,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.53,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna become the Wizard King, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:55.95,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.07,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.37,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.75,flashbackitalics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:04.63,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You mean {\i1}you{\i0} remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:08.30,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were just making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:12.84,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in being \Ntoo friendly with my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:17.05,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who gave me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.82,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're poor, an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.60,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,or even us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:27.15,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We can become greater than anyone \Nelse in this world. And to prove that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.36,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,To make Sister and everyone else happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:40.37,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:48.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:52.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, not even close.\NI still lack the strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's still ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:59.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to chase my dream right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:05.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna hurry up and get my arms \Nall healed, get even stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm definitely gonna \Nbecome the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:14.28,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.06,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,You really were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:16.95,main,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.24,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy, nom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.32,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you guys gonna thank us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.62,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,They sure have a lot of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.35,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Too much energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:25.58,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.58,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And there are so many cute girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:32.96,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Yum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.27,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Eat as much as you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:42.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:47.68,main,Gifso,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon. We'll welcome\Nyou with open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:50.41,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, damn it! Capisce?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:53.25,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to look cool at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:56.01,main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm the strongest \Nat the Underwater Temple...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:59.87,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Charmy, how are the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun guys you caught doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:03.00,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,They're yelling something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:05.70,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,They won't be able to escape, \Nso we should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:10.69,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that a ridiculously \Npowerful binding spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.70,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Kiato! Kahono!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:16.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:19.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's magic that \Ncan heal your leg and throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:23.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to fix both of my arms, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:26.43,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be dancing on this \Nleg again in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.53,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.82,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:40.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:41.95,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:47.50,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. I can finally go see Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.86,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:51.35,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.35,0:19:53.00,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.36,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:56.20,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the yummy meals!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:58.49,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:19:59.76,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come visit sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:33.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,4 AM in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:38.15,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,On such a bad day, whispering \N"Bye Bye Black Birds"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:42.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't make my anxiety go away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:44.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,for hours, lately
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:48.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been crying for hours Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:53.12,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:59.17,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All those letters that you gave to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:05.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I read them again, the pain's gone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:11.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not alone, cause we're perfect as four
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:17.64,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're far apart, \Nwe're connected, believing you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:23.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I always feel you next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:28.70,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,closer to me and a "clover" for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.40,top,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you the best of luck
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:36.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you're not alone, \Ncause we're perfect as four
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:42.17,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're far apart, \Nwe're connected, you live in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:48.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:53.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,closer to me and a "clover" for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you the best of luck
