Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.64,0:23:02.31,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:06.78,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Bah-ha Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:06.78,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.41,main,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,So I worked really hard saving all \Nthe Magic Knights on Raquey Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:18.89,sign_33433_340_Surprisingly_Tru,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1500)}Surprisingly true
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:16.25,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,Bah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:19.78,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I even got a star from the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:21.93,top,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know what to do with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:24.11,sign_33433_340_Surprisingly_Tru,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1500)}Amazingly, also true
